📆 Flask Calendar App
A web-based calendar application built with Flask, WTForms, PostgreSQL, and Jinja2. Lets users create and view appointments for a given day.

🚀 Features
Add daily appointments with:

Start & end date/time

Description and privacy setting

Form validation with custom date-time checks

PostgreSQL database integration

Clean HTML templates using Jinja2

📸 Screenshots
(Optional – drop in 1–2 screenshots of the form and the calendar view here)

🛠️ Tech Stack
Python 3.9+

Flask

PostgreSQL

psycopg2

WTForms

