Set up environment variables

Create a .env file or set the following in your terminal:

ini
Copy
Edit
DB_USER=your_user
DB_PASS=your_pass
DB_NAME=your_db
DB_HOST=localhost
Initialize the database

Run the SQL schema:

bash
Copy
Edit
psql -U your_user -d your_db -f app/database_init.sql
Start the app

bash
Copy
Edit
